message.entry: Not enough input arguments for use with RGB images.
Contrast limits {0} must be a 2-element vector.
Contrast limits {0} must be a 2-element vector or a 2-by-3 matrix.
LOW_IN must be less than HIGH_IN.
LOW_IN, HIGH_IN, LOW_OUT and HIGH_OUT must all be in the range [0, 1].
Gamma must be a scalar or a 3-element vector for RGB images.
Image must be an RGB, grayscale or colormap image.
